```python
reg = linear_model.LinearRegression()
reg.fit(df[["year"]], df["per capita income (US$)"])
```




    LinearRegression()




```python
df_income = pd.DataFrame([2020, 2021, 2022, 2023, 2024], columns=["year"])
df_income.insert(1, "per capita income (US$)", reg.predict(df_income))
df_income
```




